com.complexible.stardog.api.impl
Class DatabaseNamespaces

java.lang.Object
  com.complexible.stardog.api.impl.DatabaseNamespaces
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.complexible.common.rdf.model.Namespaces, Iterable<Namespace>
public final class DatabaseNamespaces
extends Object
implements com.complexible.common.rdf.model.Namespaces

Implementation of namespaces interface that uses database metadata for storing the namespaces. This class takes a snapshot of the namespaces stored in the database at creation time so iteration over namespaces does not require to query the database metadata again. Modifications are performed on the local copy first and then applied to the database metadata at once overriding any changes that might have occurred after the snapshot was created.

Version:
2.0
Author:
Evren Sirin, Michael Grove
